=== Etymology ===
From French ''dette''. The spelling includes the unpronounced "b", but this is an attempt to go to the original root in Latin [[debitum]]. 

===Pronunciation===
/d&#603;t/

== [[noun]] ==
#Money that one person or entity is required to pay to another, generally as a result of a loan or other monetary transaction. 

